router need to be config to work

conf t
int g0/0/0/0
no shutdown (ints are admin down by deafult)
ip addr 192.168.1.1 255.255.255.0 the ip of the network its connected to

###set up an dhcp server
router(config) ip dhcp excluded-address 192.168.1.1 192.168.1.10
router(config) ip dhcp pool SIGMA_POOL
router(dhcp-config) network 192.168.1.0 255.255.255.0
router(dhcp-config)  default-router 192.168.1.1
router(dhcp-config)  dns-server 8.8.8.8
router(dhcp-config) domain-name brain.rot67

##USEFUL DHCP COMMANDS
router # show ip dhcp binding
        show ip dhcp pool


connect the router to another router
connect using 255.255.255.252 mask
assign either .1 or .2

Add static route of the next hop for networks you are trying to go to
ip route 192.168.10.0 255.255.255.0 10.10.10.1
ip route 192.168.20.0 255.255.255.0 10.10.10.1
10.10.10.1 is the next hop router int

now add a static route back from the 10.10.10.1 
ip route 10.10.1.0 255.255.255.0 10.10.10.2
